  After graduating from the Faculty of Communication, Marmara University, she worked in various commercial organizations in Turkey and undertook managerial duties. Until 2014, she continued her volunteer activities in many civil society organizations. As of January 2014, she went to Africa with the coordination of sustainable development studies carried out by Sen De Gel Association in the least developed countries. She is currently working as the general coordinator of Sen De Gel Association.
